YOUR AROMA JOURNEY AWAITS. CHOOSE YOUR DESTINATION.













JAPAN


NEW mihana™ pure-fume™ hair mist
	Breathe in the sensual, sacred forests and gardens of Japan where citrus mingles with spice. 
	 

DISCOVER MIHANA™











BRAZIL


NEW marassona™ pure-fume™ hair mist
	Breathe in the enchancting scents of Brazil's magical coastline where the forest meets the sea. 
	 

DISCOVER MARASSONA™











MIDDLE EAST


NEW alanara™ pure-fume™ hair mist
	Breathe in the rich island woods of the ancient Fertile Crescent valley of the Middle East where spices and blossoms collide. 
	 

DISCOVER ALANARA™

































ANIMALS AND AVEDA


Aveda is a cruelty-free brand. We do not test on animals and never ask others to do so on our behalf. Our products are "people-tested."




              LEARN MORE
            


































FEEL THE
	CARE


Free today and every day: stress-relieving experiences, only 3-5 minutes. Stop in anytime.
 
 




        LEARN MORE
      














MEET MR. CHAKRA


Discover the beauty of a balanced life with a little help from Mr. Chakra and our guided meditations.
 




        LEARN MORE
      














FIND A LOCATION


Let us transport and transform you at our salons, spas and stores. Personalized services and stress-relieving rituals await you.
	 




        LEARN MORE
      




































OUR MISSION
 


OUR MISSION AT AVEDA IS TO CARE FOR THE WORLD WE LIVE IN, FROM THE PRODUCTS WE MAKE TO THE WAYS IN WHICH WE GIVE BACK TO SOCIETY. AT AVEDA, WE STRIVE TO SET AN EXAMPLE FOR ENVIRONMENTAL LEADERSHIP AND RESPONSIBILITY, NOT JUST IN THE WORLD OF BEAUTY, BUT AROUND THE WORLD.
 


HORST RECHELBACHER, FOUNDER




              LEARN MORE
            















 












 










 
























