NEW REFLECTION Me, My Color, My Care
Kérastase is breaking new ground in color care, reformulating the Reflection range and elevating it to new levels of personalization with a pioneering innovation in chromatic correction: Les Touches Chromatiques, the 1st color correcting ink-in-care for color-treated hair. 

													DISCOVER REFLECTION													


WHEN NATURE'S RAW POWER BECOMES A REFINED EXPERIENCE NEW AURA BOTANICA
98% natural origin haircare Hand-pressed Samoan coconut & argan oils Responsibly sourced actives No silicones, No sulfates Remarkable, healthy glowing hair 

													DISCOVER AURA BOTANICA													


WHEN NATURE'S RAW POWER BECOMES A REFINED EXPERIENCE NEW AURA BOTANICA
98% natural origin haircare Hand-pressed Samoan coconut & argan oils Responsibly sourced actives No silicones, No sulfates Remarkable, healthy glowing hair 

													DISCOVER AURA BOTANICA													


YOUR SMART HAIR BRUSH KERASTASE HAIR COACH
Kérastase and Withings unveil the world’s first Smart Hairbrush - created to measure the quality of your hair, the effects of different hair care routines and provide personalized advice. 

													DISCOVER													


ABOUT US  Very personal care for exceptional hair
When women speak, Kérastase listens. Follow our journey and pursuit to reveal every woman's signature identity: her hair. 

													Find out more													












Your Kérastase salon








THE FINEST HAIR CARE, DELIVERED BY A PROFESSIONAL
Kérastase is in the world’s most luxurious salons and used by the world’s best hairdressers, from Paris, New York and London to Milan, Tokyo and Rio.These magnificent spaces feature luxurious materials to express the values of sophistication, advanced science and sensorial pleasure embodied by Kérastase.
LOCATE THE NEAREST KÉRASTASE SALON








