#timelessdivaTIMELESSDIVA


#simplydivineSIMPLYDIVINE


#everblondeverblond



 


The style that is defined by its details. Where there are no limits of space or of time. Those women who have left their mark in their essence of being a Diva. Divine. Distinctive.Iconic. Sensual and bewitching, admired and emulated by all the women who have ever wanted to look like them.
Definitions of beauty that every woman adapts to fit their own personality. It makes them and shapes them according to their own nature.
 
DISCOVER THE NEW COLLECTION by RICA














The quality of a product is often compromised by incorrect use, that’s why Rica has invested in a widespread Education Program and Technical Training initiatives at various teaching levels. Managed thanks to the new artistic team, led by Antonio Musumeci, Rica Artistic Director.










